2025-12-25 13:51:21.649 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (129ms) [Parameters=[@__userId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."Id" = @__userId_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

    SELECT p."Id", p."Body", p."CreatedAt", p."DeletedAt", p."IsDeleted", p."Status", p."UpdatedAt", p."UserId"
    FROM "Posts" AS p
    WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND p."UserId" IN (
        SELECT f."FollowingId"
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."FollowerId" = @__userId_0
    )
    ORDER BY p."CreatedAt" DESC, p."Id" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS p0
INNER JOIN "Users" AS u ON p0."UserId" = u."Id"
LEFT JOIN "Likes" AS l ON p0."Id" = l."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c."Id", c."Body", c."CreatedAt", c."DeletedAt", c."IsDeleted", c."PostId", c."UpdatedAt", c."UserId", r."CommentId", CASE
        WHEN r."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN 'CommentResponse'
    END AS "Discriminator"
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    LEFT JOIN "Responses" AS r ON c."Id" = r."Id"
) AS s ON p0."Id" = s."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "PostBrutals" AS p1 ON p0."Id" = p1."PostId"
LEFT JOIN "PostImages" AS p2 ON p0."Id" = p2."PostId"
ORDER BY p0."CreatedAt" DESC, p0."Id" DESC, u."Id", l."Id", s."Id", p1."Id"

    FROM "Posts" AS p
    WHERE NOT (p."IsDeleted") AND p."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND p."UserId" IN (
        SELECT f."FollowingId"
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND f."FollowerId" = @__userId_0
    )
    ORDER BY p."CreatedAt" DESC, p."Id" DESC
    LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1
) AS p0
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT u."Id", u."CreatedAt", u."DeletedAt", u."Email", u."FirstName", u."IsDeleted", u."LastName", u."PasswordHash", u."PasswordSalt", u."RoleId", u."UpdatedAt", u."UserName"
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS u0 ON p0."UserId" = u0."Id"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT l."Id", l."CreatedAt", l."DeletedAt", l."IsDeleted", l."PostId", l."UpdatedAt", l."UserId"
    FROM "Likes" AS l
    WHERE NOT (l."IsDeleted") AND l."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS l0 ON p0."Id" = l0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c."Id", c."Body", c."CreatedAt", c."DeletedAt", c."IsDeleted", c."PostId", c."UpdatedAt", c."UserId", r."CommentId", CASE
        WHEN r."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN 'CommentResponse'
    END AS "Discriminator"
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    LEFT JOIN "Responses" AS r ON c."Id" = r."Id"

) AS s ON p0."Id" = s."PostId"

    SELECT p1."Id", p1."CreatedAt", p1."DeletedAt", p1."File", p1."IsDeleted", p1."PostId", p1."UpdatedAt"

    WHERE NOT (p1."IsDeleted") AND p1."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS p3 ON p0."Id" = p3."PostId"

    SELECT p2."Id", p2."CreatedAt", p2."DeletedAt", p2."File", p2."IsDeleted", p2."PostId", p2."UpdatedAt"
    FROM "PostImages" AS p2
    WHERE NOT (p2."IsDeleted") AND p2."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS p4 ON p0."Id" = p4."PostId"

    SELECT l."Id", l."CreatedAt", l."DeletedAt", l."IsDeleted", l."PostId", l."UpdatedAt", l."UserId"
    FROM "Likes" AS l
    WHERE NOT (l."IsDeleted") AND l."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS l0 ON p0."Id" = l0."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT c."Id", c."Body", c."CreatedAt", c."DeletedAt", c."IsDeleted", c."PostId", c."UpdatedAt", c."UserId", r."CommentId", CASE
        WHEN r."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN 'CommentResponse'
    END AS "Discriminator"
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    LEFT JOIN "Responses" AS r ON c."Id" = r."Id"
    WHERE NOT (c."IsDeleted") AND c."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS s ON p0."Id" = s."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."Id", p1."CreatedAt", p1."DeletedAt", p1."File", p1."IsDeleted", p1."PostId", p1."UpdatedAt"
    FROM "PostBrutals" AS p1
    WHERE NOT (p1."IsDeleted") AND p1."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS p3 ON p0."Id" = p3."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."Id", p2."CreatedAt", p2."DeletedAt", p2."File", p2."IsDeleted", p2."PostId", p2."UpdatedAt"
    FROM "PostImages" AS p2
    WHERE NOT (p2."IsDeleted") AND p2."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS p4 ON p0."Id" = p4."PostId"
ORDER BY p0."CreatedAt" DESC, p0."Id" DESC, u0."Id", l0."Id", s."Id", p3."Id"

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE NOT (f0."IsDeleted") AND f0."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
        WHERE NOT (f1."IsDeleted") AND f1."DeletedAt" IS NULL
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
        WHERE NOT (f2."IsDeleted") AND f2."DeletedAt" IS NULL
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

FROM "Posts" AS p

    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE NOT (f0."IsDeleted") AND f0."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0

) AS u0

    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"

    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"

    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE NOT (f0."IsDeleted") AND f0."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
        WHERE NOT (f1."IsDeleted") AND f1."DeletedAt" IS NULL
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
        WHERE NOT (f2."IsDeleted") AND f2."DeletedAt" IS NULL
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE NOT (f0."IsDeleted") AND f0."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
        WHERE NOT (f1."IsDeleted") AND f1."DeletedAt" IS NULL
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
        WHERE NOT (f2."IsDeleted") AND f2."DeletedAt" IS NULL
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"

SELECT u0."Id", u0."FirstName", u0."LastName", u0."UserName", u0.c, u0.c0, f4."Id", f4."Id0", f6."Id", f6."Id0"
FROM (
    SELECT u."Id", u."FirstName", u."LastName", u."UserName", (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f
        WHERE NOT (f."IsDeleted") AND f."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f."FollowingId") AS c, (
        SELECT count(*)::int
        FROM "Follows" AS f0
        WHERE NOT (f0."IsDeleted") AND f0."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."Id" = f0."FollowerId") AS c0
    FROM "Users" AS u
    WHERE NOT (u."IsDeleted") AND u."DeletedAt" IS NULL AND u."UserName" = @__userName_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS u0
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f3."Id", f3."Id0", f3."FollowingId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f1."FollowerId" AS "Id", f1."Id" AS "Id0", f1."FollowingId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f1."FollowingId" ORDER BY f1."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f1
        WHERE NOT (f1."IsDeleted") AND f1."DeletedAt" IS NULL
    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
        WHERE NOT (f2."IsDeleted") AND f2."DeletedAt" IS NULL
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

    ) AS f3
    WHERE f3.row <= 10
) AS f4 ON u0."Id" = f4."FollowingId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT f5."Id", f5."Id0", f5."FollowerId"
    FROM (
        SELECT f2."FollowingId" AS "Id", f2."Id" AS "Id0", f2."FollowerId", ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY f2."FollowerId" ORDER BY f2."Id" DESC) AS row
        FROM "Follows" AS f2
        WHERE NOT (f2."IsDeleted") AND f2."DeletedAt" IS NULL
    ) AS f5
    WHERE f5.row <= 10
) AS f6 ON u0."Id" = f6."FollowerId"
ORDER BY u0."Id", f4."FollowingId", f4."Id0" DESC, f6."FollowerId", f6."Id0" DESC

    SELECT c."Id", c."Body", c."CreatedAt", c."DeletedAt", c."IsDeleted", c."PostId", c."UpdatedAt", c."UserId", r."CommentId", CASE
        WHEN r."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN 'CommentResponse'
    END AS "Discriminator"
    FROM "Comments" AS c
    LEFT JOIN "Responses" AS r ON c."Id" = r."Id"
    WHERE NOT (c."IsDeleted") AND c."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS s ON p0."Id" = s."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p1."Id", p1."CreatedAt", p1."DeletedAt", p1."File", p1."IsDeleted", p1."PostId", p1."UpdatedAt"
    FROM "PostBrutals" AS p1
    WHERE NOT (p1."IsDeleted") AND p1."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS p3 ON p0."Id" = p3."PostId"
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT p2."Id", p2."CreatedAt", p2."DeletedAt", p2."File", p2."IsDeleted", p2."PostId", p2."UpdatedAt"
    FROM "PostImages" AS p2
    WHERE NOT (p2."IsDeleted") AND p2."DeletedAt" IS NULL
) AS p4 ON p0."Id" = p4."PostId"
ORDER BY p0."CreatedAt" DESC, p0."Id" DESC, u0."Id", l0."Id", s."Id", p3."Id"
